title: Billboard 200 Chart Moves Indie Country Singer Kane Brown Breaks Into Top 40
text:
Billboard 200 Chart Moves: Indie Country Singer Kane Brown Breaks Into Top 40 
Billboard Biz Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Billboard Artist 100 at No. 93. 
Much of Brown's popularity has been driven by his homemade performance videos on Facebook. A clip of him performing Lonestar's "Amazed" has amassed 6.9 million views on the platform, while another video of Brown singing along to his own "Used to Love You Sober" single has collected 11 million views.
